 company2 | 07-03-2023 |  1500 |             |            | 
 company2 | 07-04-2023 |  1400 |             |            | 
 company2 | 07-05-2023 |  1500 |             |            | 
 company2 | 07-06-2023 |    60 |          60 |       1200 | 07-07-2023
