 1 | 10 | 2 | 11 |     1
 1 | 10 | 2 | 12 |     0
 1 | 11 | 2 | 10 |     1
 1 | 11 | 2 | 11 |     1
 1 | 11 | 2 | 12 |     0
 1 | 12 | 2 | 10 |     0
 1 | 12 | 2 | 11 |     0
 1 | 12 | 2 | 12 |     0
(9 rows)

